{
  "texts": [
    "We then create an annotation guideline with a clear description of the clinical symptoms of depression that an annotator should look for in the tweets followed by relevant tweet examples for them including the confusing ones previously noted.",
    "We then separate a portion of 1500 samples from our DTR and provide it to the annotators along with our annotation guideline.",
    "During the annotation, we randomly assign a set of tweets multiple times to calculate test-retest reliability scores.",
    "We find annotators annotate the tweets consistently with the same annotation with 83% reliability based on the test-retest reliability score.",
    "Our detailed guideline description is provided in Appendix 3."
  ]
}